data.value:
Presyong Ka-Piyu is a convenient and user-friendly platform designed to help students, faculty, and visitors navigate the LSPU Main Campus marketplace efficiently. The application allows users to:
- Browse products and services available at various campus stores. - View store details including location, contact, description, rating, and favorite status. - Check product prices and categories, helping you make informed decisions. - Locate campus stores easily through an interactive campus map with location pins.
Our goal is to simplify campus life by providing a centralized, digital marketplace experience.
